      </div>
      <p class="footer-about mt-5 leading-relaxed text-gray-300">
        Building excellence since 2008. Ultraction General Contracting delivers innovative construction solutions with uncompromising quality and integrity.
      </p>
      <div class="social-links flex mt-6">
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 rounded-full mr-3 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-primary">
          <i class="fab fa-facebook-f text-white text-lg"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 rounded-full mr-3 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-primary">
          <i class="fab fa-twitter text-white text-lg"></i>
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 bg-white/5 rounded-full mr-3 transition-all duration-300 hover:transform hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-primary">
